'''João Felipe Schmidt Urbano''' (born 19 May 1993), known as '''João Schmidt''', is a Brazilian professional [[Association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[Midfielder#Defensive midfielder|defensive midfielder]] for [[Nagoya Grampus]].

==Club career==

===São Paulo===
Schmidt began his career with hometown club [[São Paulo FC|São Paulo]] in 2005.

{{Expand section|date=July 2017}}

====Loan to Vitória de Setúbal====
In July 2014, he made his first move abroad, joining [[Primeira Liga]] club, [[Vitória F.C.|Vitória de Setúbal]].<ref>{{cite news|title=João Schmidt: "Este clube lança muitos jogadores"|url=http://www.record.xl.pt/Futebol/Nacional/1a_liga/vitoria_setubal/interior.aspx?content_id=899245|work=Record|date=11 August 2014|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140820085343/http://www.record.xl.pt/Futebol/Nacional/1a_liga/vitoria_setubal/interior.aspx?content_id=899245|archivedate=20 August 2014}}</ref>

{{Expand section|date=July 2017}}

===Atalanta===
In July 2017, Schmidt left São Paulo for Italian side [[Atalanta B.C.|Atalanta]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.atalanta.it/site/paginalive/comunicati-dal-club/Stagione-2017-2018/2017-07/08-07-Calciomercato-ingaggiato-Schmidt.html|title=Ecco João Schmidt|last=|first=|date=8 July 2017|website=www.atalanta.it|publisher=Atalanta B.C.|language=it-IT|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170710174328/http://www.atalanta.it/site/paginalive/comunicati-dal-club/Stagione-2017-2018/2017-07/08-07-Calciomercato-ingaggiato-Schmidt.html|archive-date=10 July 2017|dead-url=yes|access-date=19 July 2017}}</ref>

====Rio Ave loan====
On 6 July 2018, Schmidt joined [[Rio Ave F.C.|Rio Ave]] on a one-year loan deal with an option to make the move permanent.<ref>{{cite web |title=João Schmidt chega da Atalanta |url=http://www.rioavefc.pt/joao-schmidt-chega-da-atalanta/ |website=rioavefc.pt/ |publisher=Rio Ave F.C. |accessdate=26 April 2019 |language=Portuguese |date=6 July 2018}}</ref> On 2 February 2019, Rio Ave and Atalanta agreed to end the loan deal early.<ref>{{cite web |title=Obrigado Schmidt |url=http://www.rioavefc.pt/obrigado-schmidt/ |website=rioavefc.pt/ |publisher=Rio Ave F.C. |accessdate=26 April 2019 |language=Portuguese |date=2 February 2019}}</ref>

===Nagoya Grampus===
On 6 February 2019, [[Nagoya Grampus]] announced the signing of Schmidt.<ref name="João Schmidt">{{cite web |title=ジョアン シミッチ選手、移籍加入のお知らせ |url=http://nagoya-grampus.jp/news/pressrelease/2019/0206post-1147.php |website=nagoya-grampus.jp |publisher=Nagoya Grampus |accessdate=6 February 2019 |language=Japanese |date=6 February 2019}}</ref>

